						<div class="postbody">Hey. Been working away on a wee platformer thing using Construct 2. I have no coding skills whatsoever, I just enjoy messing with the oul' pixels. I love the look of NES games. Love all the blacks n' the chunky low resolution. I wanted to emulate that, but not stick 100% within the NES's limits. Was wondering what a group of NES experts thought of how my game's coming along so far. Any crits, comments or suggestions would be greatly appreciated.</div>

					
